      <title>六场风暴即将来袭，澳大利亚做好应对威胁生命的洪水的准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/australia-braces-for-life-threatening-floods-as-six-storms-brew</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计未来几天澳大利亚及其领土周围的六场风暴将增强，其中一个系统可能会在该国北部引发危及生命的洪水，另外三个系统至少有中等可能性在周一形成热带气旋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/australia-braces-for-life-threatening-floods-as-six-storms-brew</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 05:12:42 GMT</pubDate>
